metadata.description:
e9Art - AI Portraits (the weird & the wonderful)


in the rapidly changing world of AI, i already find myself waxing nostalgic about the earlier, less perfect, versions of AI art tools. 

i love their unpredictable interpretations and flawed renderings, especially of the human form…

and i wanted to document that on the blockchain … to record this fleeting, ephemeral moment of these (beautiful?) imperfections …

of the AI art tools … and perhaps also, of my own.

digital art by e9Art using disco diffusion 5.6,  photoshop, et al. August 2022.
